      "value": "<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.Dysu4F8licjEb2FY]{Vanguard Discipline}</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DetailedOutput\"> Your entropic strike can be virulent to your foes. When you successfully hit a creature with your entropic strike, you can spend 1 Entropy Point to infect it with a mote of entropic virulence until the end of your next turn (Fortitude negates). While the creature is infected and within your entropic strike&rsquo;s melee reach, you can make entropic strike attacks that originate from the infected creature&rsquo;s space on your turn. You can&rsquo;t make attacks of opportunity from the infected creature&rsquo;s space.</span></p>"
